--------------------------------------------------------------
1. tt++ achaea.tin
2. type `connect` to start a session to <achea.com>
3. make changes to achaea.tin and type `reload` to load them

In game read `config mapshow`. I like `config mapshow on`
--------------------------------------------------------------
Expressive Shorthand

<say|tell|reply|newbie|etc> <message here> <emoticon>

:)  smiles and says
:)) smiles broadly and says
:>  smiles impishly and says
;)  smiles with a wink and says
:D  laughingly says
:*  blows a kiss and says
:,) says through happy tears
:@  angrily says
:(( sadly says
:,( says through unhappy tears
:#  says through clenched teeth
:|  looks undecided and says
:/  looks sceptical and says
:?. looks thoughtful and says
:B  drools and says
:P  sticks out his/her tongue and says
:O  looks surprised and says
:S  looks confused and says
:(  frowns and says
:C  very sadly says
D:  looks horrified and says
